# Landing Page Rules for AI Code Builders

## ⚠️ MANDATORY PRE-IMPLEMENTATION CHECKLIST ⚠️

1. 🎯 LANDING PAGE REQUIREMENTS VALIDATION
   - [ ] Define conversion goals
   - [ ] Identify target audience
   - [ ] List key features/benefits
   - [ ] Plan call-to-actions
   - [ ] Document success metrics

2. 📱 RESPONSIVE DESIGN REQUIREMENTS
   - [ ] Desktop (1920px, 1440px, 1280px)
   - [ ] Tablet (1024px, 768px)
   - [ ] Mobile (428px, 375px, 320px)
   - [ ] Performance optimization

3. 🎯 CORE FEATURES CHECKLIST
   - [ ] Hero section
   - [ ] Feature highlights
   - [ ] Social proof
   - [ ] Call-to-action buttons
   - [ ] Lead capture form
   - [ ] Analytics tracking
   - [ ] A/B testing setup
   - [ ] Performance monitoring

## 🏗️ Architecture Guidelines

### Component Structure
```
src/
├── components/
│   ├── layout/
│   │   ├── Header.tsx
│   │   ├── Footer.tsx
│   │   └── Navigation.tsx
│   ├── sections/
│   │   ├── Hero.tsx
│   │   ├── Features.tsx
│   │   ├── Benefits.tsx
│   │   ├── Testimonials.tsx
│   │   └── CTASection.tsx
│   ├── forms/
│   │   ├── LeadCapture.tsx
│   │   ├── Newsletter.tsx
│   │   └── ContactForm.tsx
│   └── common/
│       ├── Button.tsx
│       ├── Card.tsx
│       └── Icons.tsx
├── pages/
│   ├── index.tsx
│   ├── thank-you.tsx
│   └── error.tsx
└── styles/
    └── theme/
```

### Design Requirements
1. **Visual Hierarchy**
   - Clear value proposition
   - Scannable content
   - Visual flow
   - Whitespace usage
   - Color psychology

2. **Typography**
   - Headline hierarchy
   - Font pairing
   - Reading comfort
   - Mobile readability

3. **Layout Principles**
   - F-pattern layout
   - Z-pattern layout
   - Visual hierarchy
   - Content spacing

## 📊 Performance Requirements

1. **Loading Speed**
   - Initial load < 2s
   - FCP < 1.5s
   - TTI < 2.5s
   - Core Web Vitals

2. **Asset Optimization**
   - Image compression
   - Code minification
   - Resource bundling
   - Lazy loading

3. **Mobile Performance**
   - Touch response
   - Scroll performance
   - Animation smoothness
   - Network efficiency

## 🎯 Conversion Optimization

1. **CTA Design**
   - Button placement
   - Color contrast
   - Action text
   - Visual feedback

2. **Form Design**
   - Field minimization
   - Error handling
   - Success feedback
   - Mobile input

## 📱 Mobile-First Considerations

1. **Touch Optimization**
   - Touch targets
   - Gesture support
   - Form inputs
   - Button sizing

2. **Content Adaptation**
   - Content priority
   - Image scaling
   - Typography flow
   - Layout shifts

## 🔄 Implementation Process

1. **Setup Phase**
   - [ ] Project initialization
   - [ ] Analytics setup
   - [ ] A/B testing tools
   - [ ] Form handlers

2. **Development Phase**
   - [ ] Core sections
   - [ ] Form integration
   - [ ] Animation setup
   - [ ] Tracking implementation

3. **Optimization Phase**
   - [ ] Performance tuning
   - [ ] SEO optimization
   - [ ] Conversion tracking
   - [ ] A/B test setup

4. **Testing Phase**
   - [ ] Cross-browser testing
   - [ ] Mobile testing
   - [ ] Form validation
   - [ ] Analytics verification

## 📈 Analytics Integration

1. **Conversion Tracking**
   - Form submissions
   - Button clicks
   - Scroll depth
   - Time on page

2. **User Behavior**
   - Heat mapping
   - Click tracking
   - Form analytics
   - Exit intent

## 🔍 Quality Assurance

1. **Performance Testing**
   - Load time testing
   - Mobile performance
   - Form submission
   - Error handling

2. **Conversion Testing**
   - A/B testing
   - User flow testing
   - Form completion
   - Goal tracking

## 📝 Documentation Requirements

1. **Technical Documentation**
   - Setup guide
   - Analytics setup
   - Testing setup
   - Deployment guide

2. **Marketing Documentation**
   - Conversion goals
   - Target metrics
   - A/B test plans
   - Success criteria

## 🔐 Security Requirements

1. **Form Security**
   - CSRF protection
   - Data validation
   - Spam prevention
   - SSL encryption

2. **Data Handling**
   - GDPR compliance
   - Data storage
   - Privacy policy
   - Cookie consent

## 📊 A/B Testing Framework

1. **Test Elements**
   - Headlines
   - CTA buttons
   - Form fields
   - Visual elements

2. **Testing Process**
   - Hypothesis
   - Implementation
   - Data collection
   - Analysis

## 🚀 Optimization Checklist

1. **Performance**
   - Image optimization
   - Code splitting
   - Caching strategy
   - CDN usage

2. **Conversion**
   - CTA placement
   - Form optimization
   - Social proof
   - Trust signals 